{"tid":1447012,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"輸?放棄?失敗?  香港一日比一日黑暗","createTime":"2019-08-11T15:30:07.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-11T18:43:05.000Z","uid":262261,"like":15,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"2ddd74810a8bdf2c69cc59d0a1872b5b55ae246b","tid":1447012,"uid":262261,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T15:30:07.000Z","msg":"有人話612係香港最黑暗嘅一日<br />\n直到721<br />\n又有人話<br />\n今日係香港最黑暗嘅一日<br />\n再到左今日<br />\n再次有人話 今日係香港最黑暗嘅一日<br />\n你地覺得呢 邊一日先係香港最黑暗嘅一日？<br />\n<br />\n對我黎講 當我地都放棄嘅時候 當無人再企出黎嘅個一日 無人再為香港發聲嘅個一日 先係 香港最黑暗嘅個一日<br />\n所以唔好再講咩輸 咩放棄 咩失敗啊 <br />\n有好多人為左我地而犧牲<br />\n受傷 崖餓 被捕 失去視力 失去生命......<br />\n我知道大家都好嬲 有好多意見 有就多不滿 （對自己人）但希望大家可以冷靜啲 團結啲 唔好再互屌啊 <br />\n要屌都係屌班狗 屌班高官 屌班無人性嘅藍絲<br />\n<br />\n大家一齊行落去 好唔好啊......"},{"pid":"fc654cf892379099650bb99cd18fb7530c14ce84","tid":1447012,"uid":262261,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T15:32:01.000Z","msg":"團結"},{"pid":"502ae2ac7cd20c488f6d6babd64d448d98baad6b","tid":1447012,"uid":262261,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T15:32:18.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3a23daddca996e4104382fb8bafb44d463cdb122","tid":1447012,"uid":262261,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T15:32:30.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e3190f76c971861d4164c104a28bd769d5829b4c","tid":1447012,"uid":262261,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T15:32:41.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0cd4f0d8c04eab65dd456972b31c703dd075f9b0","tid":1447012,"uid":262261,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T15:32:51.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e01b1e54a7897bb86495e00a15e7a17ae2f22341","tid":1447012,"uid":32719,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T15:32:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XDeNsSM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXDeNsSM.jpg&h=ec2e27ab&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NxxbUxN.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"ht